---------------------------------------------------------
padded/leather armor                              8
---------------------------------------------------------
padded/leather armor + shield,
studded or ring mail                              7
---------------------------------------------------------
studded/ringmail + shield,
brigandine,
scale mail,
or hide armor                                     6
---------------------------------------------------------
scale mail / hide + shield,
chain mail                                        5
---------------------------------------------------------
chain mail + shield
splint mail,
banded mail,
or bronze plate
mail                                              4
---------------------------------------------------------
splint, banded, or bronze plate + shield
or plate mail                                     3
---------------------------------------------------------
plate mail and shield
field plate                                       2
---------------------------------------------------------
field plate + shield,
full plate                                        1
---------------------------------------------------------
full plate + shield                               0
---------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------

AC Range is +10 to -10  (+10 = easy to hit)
Magical armor will allow for ac lower than 0

